## Aba balekabila icifulo ukwakwikala
## Nibanani abailimba muli uyu mulimo?
## Twaba amayanda yabili fwebantungulula uyu mulimo: Ba Kelvin naba Joyce Samwata elyo naba Philip Cole nabena mwabo ba Deborah. 
